### Crear un producto
POST {{host}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Queso duro llanero churro 9",
  "price": 10,
  "priceSale": 13.99,
  "stock": 10,
  "images": [
    "http://image1.jgp",
    "http://image2.jgp"
  ]
}

